> "Open fire against this Saberback ans his dinosaurs!!!!" yelled
> Hydras"Cyclonus, set the defences and open fire against Saberback".

"Of course." CYCLONUS said as he relayed HYDRAS' command back to the base.

After a few moments the base as well as CYCLONUS and the soldiers that
HYDRAS had brought with him also opened fire on the Dinosaurs!

Quickly the first row of Dinisaurs were killed, and then the second,
and then the third, and even the fourth but there were literally
thousands of them. Missile weapons from the ship had a little more
effect as it hit them closer to the center, but that only created a
hole of death that was quickly filled in by the running dinosaurs -
they seemed to have no recognition that this was resulting in their
death.

"Ahh yes the typcial Decepticon and Predfacon response." SABERBACK
said with bemuesement over the radio to HYDRAS. In the distance
weapons fire was aimed at SABERBACK but it was bouncing off some
personal forcefield that he had up.

"Sir." FRACTYL transmitted to HYDRAS again, "We are picking up some
sort of harmonic pulse that that being seems to be using to control
the Dinosaurs."
